A '''yayax''' was a beast that lived on the moon of [[Endor/Legends|Endor]]. During the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], a [[Clone commando/Legends|clone commando]] unit was named [[Yayax Squad]].

While on the planet [[Mimban/Legends|Mimban]]<ref name="Splinter of the Mind's Eye 1">[[Splinter of the Mind's Eye 1|''Splinter of the Mind's Eye'' 1]]</ref> in the [[Standard year/Legends|year]] [[2 ABY/Legends|2 ABY]],<ref name="The Essential Reader's Companion">''[[The Essential Reader's Companion]]'' dates the events of the novel ''[[Splinter of the Mind's Eye]]'' to the [[Standard year/Legends|year]] [[2 ABY/Legends|2 ABY]]. As it is an adaptation of part of the novel, [[Splinter of the Mind's Eye 1|''Splinter of the Mind's Eye'' 1]] must also take place in 2 [[Galactic Standard Calendar|ABY]].</ref> the [[Protocol droid/Legends|protocol droid]] [[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]] assumed a hideous shriek he could hear from the [[Jungle/Legends|jungle]] was a hunger-crazed Endorian yayax that was coming to eat [[Gender/Legends|himself]] and fellow [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] member [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]].<ref name="Splinter of the Mind's Eye 1" />

